    - pfp
		- account name
		- username
    - hrs ago tweeted
    - more button
    - tweet body
    - comments, retweets, likes, views, share.

----- THIRD
  - a search bar which is mixed
  - what's happening section.
  - who to follow section.
  - small message box which is fixed.
